        function onChartAssetLoad(configs) {
  createChart(configs);
  window.removeEventListener("YFINCHART_SRC_LOAD", onChartAssetLoad);
};
        function getChartConfig(configs) {
  const {
    chartTypeOverride = "",
    chartRange,
    quoteType,
    exchange,
    lang,
    region,
    shouldUseUpdatedBeacon,
    storedChartType,
    studies,
    theme,
    featureFlags
  } = configs;
  const extendedHours = hasExtendedHours(quoteType, exchange);
  const { extendedHoursEnabled } = initialChartSettings();
  const chartType = chartTypeOverride ? chartTypeOverride : storedChartType;
  return {
    chartRange: chartRange || INITIAL_SPAN,
    container: document.querySelector(".chartContainer"),
    disableGridLines: {
      x: true
    },
    enableEventsQuote: false,
    featureFlags,
    layout: {
      chartType,
      extended: extendedHours ? extendedHoursEnabled : false,
      padding: 20
    },
    quoteFeed: {
      lang,
      region
    },
    shouldUseUpdatedBeacon,
    showExtededHours: extendedHours ? extendedHoursEnabled : false,
    studies,
    theme: theme || "light",
    onRapidEvent
  };
};
        function createChart(configs) {
  if (!window.finQuoteChart) {
    toggleOverlay(true);
    const chartConfig = getChartConfig(configs);
    window.finQuoteChart = new window.YFinChart.QuoteChart({
      ...chartConfig
    });
    loadChart(configs);
  }
};
        function loadChart(configs) {
  let quoteChartLoad = void 0;
  let quoteChartRender = void 0;
  const {
    chartRange,
    quoteType,
    symbol,
    loadQuoteCB,
    comparisonSymbol,
    periodicties,
    spans,
    beaconPerf,
    enableQSPChartToolbarCleanup,
    storedShowKeyEvent,
    storedAnalystRatingsKeyEvent,
    storedEarningsKeyEvent
  } = configs;
  if (window.finQuoteChart) {
    const span = chartRange || getInitialSpan(quoteType);
    const interval = getInitialInterval(span);
    window.finQuoteChart.loadChart(
      symbol,
      {
        interval: periodicties[interval],
        span: spans[span]
      },
      (err, stx) => {
        if (err) {
          console.error(err);
          return;
        }
        restoreChartSettings();
        toggleOverlay(false);
        quoteChartRender = Date.now();
        const startTime = window?.finNeoPageStart;
        if (quoteChartLoad && quoteChartRender && startTime) {
          const func = new Function(`return ${beaconPerf}`)();
          func({
            "fin-qsp-chart-load": quoteChartLoad - startTime,
            "fin-qsp-chart-render": quoteChartRender - startTime
          });
        }
        window.chartHasData = stx.chart.dataSegment.length > 0;
        if (loadQuoteCB) {
          const cb = new Function(`return ${loadQuoteCB}`)();
          cb(comparisonSymbol.symbol);
        }
        const showEvent = enableQSPChartToolbarCleanup ? storedEarningsKeyEvent : storedShowKeyEvent;
        const additionalEvent = enableQSPChartToolbarCleanup ? storedAnalystRatingsKeyEvent : storedShowKeyEvent;
        window.finQuoteChart.showEventsQuote(showEvent, additionalEvent);
      }
    );
    quoteChartLoad = Date.now();
  }
};
        function isMobileChart(width) {
  return width <= CHART_1D_MAX_WIDTH;
};
        function getInitialSpan(quoteType) {
  const isMobile = isMobileChart(window.finQuoteChart.stx.chart.canvasWidth);
  if (["MUTUALFUND", "CUL_IDX", "CUL_SUB_IDX"].indexOf(quoteType) > -1) {
    return isMobile ? "1m-sm" : "1m";
  }
  return isMobile ? INITIAL_SPAN_SM : INITIAL_SPAN;
};
        function getInitialInterval(span) {
  const isMobile = isMobileChart(window.finQuoteChart.stx.chart.canvasWidth);
  if (span === "1mo") {
    return isMobile ? "12h" : "1d";
  }
  return isMobile ? "5m" : "1m";
};
        function setChartSetting(settingName, value) {
  switch (settingName) {
    case "tooltipEnabled":
      window.finQuoteChart.stx.layout.headsUp = { floating: value };
      break;
    case "extendedHoursEnabled":
      window.finQuoteChart.setExtendedHours(value);
      break;
  }
};
        function getLSChartSettings() {
  const defaultSettings = {
    extendedHoursEnabled: true,
    tooltipEnabled: true
  };
  if (isLocalStorageSupported) {
    try {
      const lsSettings = window.localStorage.getItem(LS_SETTINGS_KEY);
      if (lsSettings === null) {
        return defaultSettings;
      }
      return JSON.parse(lsSettings);
    } catch (err) {
    }
  }
  return defaultSettings;
};
        function toggleOverlay(shouldShow) {
  const overlay = document.getElementsByClassName("loadingOverlay")[0];
  if (overlay) {
    const value = shouldShow ? "flex" : "none";
    overlay.style.display = value;
  }
}        
        function initialChartSettings() {
  const lsSettings = getLSChartSettings();
  if (isLocalStorageSupported) {
    window.localStorage.setItem(LS_SETTINGS_KEY, JSON.stringify(lsSettings));
  }
  return lsSettings;
}
        function hasExtendedHours(quoteType, exchange) {
  return ["EQUITY", "ETF"].indexOf(quoteType.toUpperCase()) > -1 && ["ASE", "NAS", "NXX", "NMS", "NYQ", "NYS", "PCX", "NCM", "NGM", "BTS"].indexOf(
    exchange.toUpperCase()
  ) > -1;
}
        function restoreChartSettings() {
  const lsSettings = getLSChartSettings();
  setChartSetting("tooltipEnabled", lsSettings.tooltipEnabled);
}
        function onRapidEvent(event) {
  const beacon = window.rapidInstance?.beaconClick;
  const sec = "qsp-chart-keyevent";
  switch (event) {
    case "eventsQuote-clickRight":
      beacon(sec, "next", 0, { itc: 1, elm: "arrow" });
      break;
    case "eventsQuote-clickLeft":
      beacon(sec, "prev", 0, { itc: 1, elm: "arrow" });
      break;
    case "eventsQuote-hover":
      beacon(sec, "key-event", 0, { itc: 2, elm: "event" });
      break;
  }
}
        const initializeChart = function initializeChart(configs) {
  if (!window.finQuoteChart && window.YFinChart?.QuoteChart) {
    onChartAssetLoad(configs);
  } else {
    window.addEventListener("YFINCHART_SRC_LOAD", () => {
      onChartAssetLoad(configs);
    });
  }
};
        const INITIAL_SPAN = '1d-qsp';
        const INITIAL_SPAN_SM = '1d-sm';
        const CHART_1D_MAX_WIDTH = '480';
        const LS_SETTINGS_KEY = 'yf-quote-chart-settings';
